OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FMany places will be dry for
OL,6,Fmost of the day with a few bright
OL,7,Fspells. Thickening cloud will bring a
OL,8,Ffew showers from the southwest later
OL,9,Fthis afternoon. Warm.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FThis evening will be cloudy
OL,12,Fwith outbreaks of rain. Remaining
OL,13,Fcloudy overnight with further spells
OL,14,Fof rain, occasionally heavy.
OL,15,FFreshening southerly wind along the
OL,16,Feast coast.
OL,17,
OL,18,CTuesday:FVariable amounts of cloud and
OL,19,Fsunny spells along with scattered slow
OL,20,Fmoving showers, occasionally heavy.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
