OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FDry
OL,6,Ffor most of Wednesday but some patchy
OL,7,Frain for a time in the afternoon. A
OL,8,Ffew early showers on Thursday,
OL,9,Fotherwise dry. Rain spreading east on
OL,10,FFriday.
